                    </a>
                </div><!-- Service Thumb /-->
                <div class="service-info">
                    <h4><a href="#">Glaucoma</a></h4>
                    <p style="text-align:justify">Glaucoma is a group of diseases that affect the optic nerve and involves a loss of retinal ganglion cells in a characteristic pattern. It is a type of optic neuropathy. Raised intraocular pressure is a significant risk factor for developing glaucoma (above 22 mmHg or 2.9 kPa). </p>
                </div><!-- Service Info /-->
            </div><!-- Service /-->
        </div><!-- Service Blog column /-->

        <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns service">
            <div class="serivce-block">
