                    </a>
                </div><!-- Service Thumb /-->
                <div class="service-info">
                    <h4><a href="#">LaSic Eye Surgery</a></h4>
                    <p style="text-align:justify">
                        LASIK or Lasik (laser-assisted in situ keratomileusis) is a type of refractive surgery for correcting myopia, hyperopia, and astigmatism.
                        LASIK is performed by ophthalmologists using a laser.<br />
                    </p>
                </div><!-- Service Info /-->
            </div><!-- Service /-->
        </div><!-- Service Blog column /-->

        <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns service">
            <div class="serivce-block">
